co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.table
Interface OrderedTable

All Superinterfaces:
Closeable, Dataset
Deprecated. since 2.8.0. Use Table instead. 

@Deprecated
public interface OrderedTable
extends Dataset

This class was previously used internally by CDAP for a generic table dataset interface. Its implementation has been replaced and is no longer used. However, since it exposed constants intended for application use, the class is retained in order to deprecate the exposed constants.
